    fr.sorbonne_u.components.ComponentI, fr.sorbonne_u.cps.smartcity.interfaces.SAMUNotificationImplI, ActionExecutionImplementationI
    public class Samu
extends fr.sorbonne_u.components.AbstractComponent
implements fr.sorbonne_u.cps.smartcity.interfaces.SAMUNotificationImplI, ActionExecutionImplementationI
    The class Samu implements a component that can emit events and execute actions

    The component implements the SAMUNotificationImplI interface to receive the notification from samu proxy component and to perform actions, it implements l'interface ActionExecutionImplementationI to execute actions that come from correlator

    作者:
    Yajie LIU, Zimeng ZHANG
